HR Administration (Sentul Based)
Responsibilities
Support day to day operation in term of manpower, support assist in personel administration work, checking day to day absent, calculate overtime, support training process. REQUIREMENTS : Candidate must possess at least a Diploma, majoring psychology/ Management.At least 1 year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.Having knowladge in HR policy & man power regulation.Having experience in warehouse operation, preferably from multinational logistics company.Good in communication skills, and people management.Computer literate (Ms. Office)Preferably Staff (non-management & non-supervisor)s specializing in Human Resources or equivalent.Applicants must be willing to work in Sentul.  Please send your resume not later than 7 (seven) days after this advertisement to :  Recruitment DHL Supply ChainE-mail : recruitment.id@dhl.com Only short-listed candidates will be contacted for further selection
